				<font face="verdana" size="2"><Blockquote>
<B><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/harpys-head/Forum9/HTML/000269.html">The Sacking of Highkeep</a></B><P>

<I>Today we tested an old event idea that was sidelined due to the changing of the guards and guildmasters in many of the cities.<P>

After review of the cities, we noticed that Highkeep was still able to be sacked if a guild was strong enough, and fast enough to accomplish it.<P>

The goal was to eliminate all guard presence in the zone of Highpass, so that not one guard was present in the zone, and advance foward into Highkeep.<P>

Highkeep would then need to be completely removed of all Guard NPC, including any respawn if needed, so that at one given time there would be NO guards in the city, anywhere in the zone.<P>

A random guild was chosen, The Mystical Order of Fennin Ro, and they were able to accomplish this task.<P>

My thanks to TMO for assisting in this test, and we will be working on a new type of event from the data collected on this test in the future.<P>

Congrats to all involved, you did your gods a great deed this evening.<P>

Lady Daegarmo</I>
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
		
