<B><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/035688.html">TV Guide</a></B><P>

<I>As most of you probably already know, EverQuest will be featured in TV Guide on December 9th.<P>

If you are interested in obtaining a copy but you don't subscribe to the magazine and you won't be able to get to a store to pick one up (say, for example, you don't live in the United States), there is a way that you can get a copy.<P>

Call 1-800-866-1400 or send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:tvg.customer.support@tvguide.com">tvg.customer.support@tvguide.com</a><P>

I've been told that it will cost $2.00 to purchase the issue this way (you will essentially be ordering a back order copy) and $3.00 to ship it internationally. But make sure to verify the cost with them when placing your order. They said that they will accept Visa, Mastercard, Discover, American Express, International Money Order or a check drawn on an American bank.<P>

EverQuest will be featured with some sort of article (I don't know what it's about) and the cover, with nice art (I don't know what the topic of the art will be either).<P>

Alan</I><P>

