				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="15">Lanys T'vyl: Qeynos Newbie Fair</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:ferret@prolynx.com">A.R. Harmon</b></a>
				[11/30/2000-6:18:34 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=287712"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[2]</font></a>
				<p>
