Hail residents of Lanys T'yvl! On Sunday, December 2 at 1pm eastern members of the Dragons Alliance guild will be hosting a newbie fair in Qeynos.  A first aid station will be set up offering heals, buffs, and refreshments.  Contests ranging from scavenger hunts to trivia questions will be held throughout the afternoon with prizes awarded to the winners.  There will be two divisions for some of the contests consisting of levels one through five and levels six through ten.
