2. The gate guards are, unlike those outside Freeport or Qeynos, are low enough in level to be hunted by groups of chars in their 30's, and often are hunted. <P>

Even the bind point for new DE chars is scarcely close to these newbie guards."<P>

<B>1. Not much further away than any other guards, really. The newbie monsters spawn pretty much at the log… I've died out there enough to know that it's a long run, sure. But the bridge is about three times as far for the real 'newbies' to run.<P>

